summary: Completed comprehensive testing of PaginiGalbui landing page feature. Fixed critical API proxy issue and verified all navigation flows work correctly.

resolved_issues.issue: Frontend could not communicate with backend - missing setupProxy.js
resolved_issues.fix_applied: Created /app/frontend/src/setupProxy.js to proxy /api requests to localhost:8001

passed_tests: Landing page displays correctly at root URL /
Animated counters show correct database counts (contacts: 2,133, passwords: 3,356, accounts: 116)
Search bar allows text input and Enter key navigation to /app?search=<query>
Search button click navigation to /app?search=<query> works
Case selector dropdown shows available cases (2025/19/P/2025, 794/19/P/2025)
Case selection navigates to /app?case=<case_number> with proper URL encoding
Browse all data link navigates to /app
Home button in main app navigates back to landing page /
URL parameters are correctly passed and applied in main app
API integration works correctly after proxy fix
Main app loads with case filtering applied
